caption.text: Celebrating with those who have disabilities and their families the passage of the ABLE Act. This bill will allow family members and citizens with disabilities to contribute up to $14,000 per year into a tax deferred account to save for medical and living expenses (similar to college savings plans). Allows for greater independence and less reliance on govt assistance. Also allows those with disabilities to earn and save money while working - without being penalized. High Fives all around ✋
